snippet.title: ShootersPool - Billiards Simulation | Official Billiards Brands Partners
snippet.description:
In ShootersPool we work with the most important billiards brands worldwide such as Rasson Billiards, JOY Billiards, OB Cues, Diamond Billiards, Predator Cues, Gabriels Billiards, Aramith Billiards Balls, Iwan Simonis Cloths and Strachan Cloths, to provide our players the most immersive game experience.

All the products from this brands has been recreated with all the details both visual and technical so the players can feel the most faithful game experience.

You are able to set your games and play with the same setting of some of the most important tournaments in the world such as the Mosconi Cup, the World Cup of Pool, the World Pool Masters, the 9 Ball Us Open, the Derby City Classic, the Snooker Champion of Champions, the Ceulemans Cup or the 3 Cushion World Championships.

You have available to play products such as the Diamond PRO-AM, the Rasson Victory II, the Rasson Magnum II, the Grabriels Rafale, the JOY Q8, the Aramith Tournament PRO-CUP TV, the Simonis 860, the Strachan N10 Championship, the REVO shafts or the OB shafts.

What are you waiting to try it? 👉http://bit.ly/2ZJyY3C

Share this video: 
👉 https://youtu.be/3GIr6_t-oNc

Subscribe to this Youtube Channel:

See you at the tables! :)
